import React from 'react';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';
import { Button, Box, Typography } from '@mui/material';

const Home = () => {
  return (
    <Box 
      sx={{ 
        display: 'flex', 
        flexDirection: 'column', 
        alignItems: 'center', 
        gap: 2, 
        padding: 4 
      }}
    >
      <Typography variant="h2" gutterBottom>
        Welcome to the App
      </Typography>

      <Box>
        <Button variant="contained" color="primary" component={Link} to="/register">
          Регистрация
        </Button>
      </Box>

      <Box>
        <Button variant="contained" color="secondary" component={Link} to="/login">
          Авторизация
        </Button>
      </Box>

      <Box>
        <Button variant="outlined" color="primary" component={Link} to="/posts">
          Новости
        </Button>
      </Box>

      <Box>
        <Button variant="outlined" color="primary" component={Link} to="/transactions">
          ТНС
        </Button>
      </Box>

      <Box>
        <Button variant="outlined" color="primary" component={Link} to="/tgks">
          ТГК
        </Button>
      </Box>

      <Box>
        <Button variant="outlined" color="primary" component={Link} to="/transactions">
          Водоканал
        </Button>
      </Box>
    </Box>
    
  );
};

export default Home;
